1.0.name: wordpress/debut
1.0.description: Debut is a solid and clean responsive theme, for sharing your ideas with the world. Make Debut your own by changing the background, colors and more with the new Theme Customizer and real-time preview. Based on _s by Automattic, Debut is translation-ready (French is already included), supports featured images, has five widget areas and includes a sliding menu for mobile screens. Debut also includes a full-width page template.
